msgstr "There is already an open inclusion request for this collection."

msgid "This community has no subcommunities"
msgstr "This collection has no child collections"

msgid "This is the community stats dashboard."
msgstr "This is the collection stats dashboard."

msgid ""
"This request has been automatically accepted, as the uploader can submit to "
"community directly without review."
msgstr ""
"This request has been automatically accepted, as the uploader can submit to "
"collection directly without review."

